{"tid":869433,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺龍心行緊大蛇丸果條路？","createTime":"2018-10-20T10:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T15:29:38.000Z","uid":123335,"like":9,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d3288e1124fcd6acf66dee01358bdb1611f0a6f0","tid":869433,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:41:50.000Z","msg":"龍心棄做正常人<br />\n出道個原意<br />\n係為左探索緊生存既意義<br />\n你見佢片中會質疑好多social norm<br />\nEg 佢有質疑過「何謂Freedom? 何謂自由？」<br />\n<br />\n龍心佢一直就係透過行動去挑戰呢啲social norm<br />\n其實佢同大蛇丸都一樣<br />\n對學術知識上都有比常人更熱切既追求<br />\n<br />\n好可惜<br />\n大蛇丸為咗追求的忍術嘅奧義<br />\n不惜大量開發禁術<br />\n龍心為咗追求social science 既奧義<br />\n連19歲既o靚妹都疑似受佢影響搞到入精神病院<br />\n根本龍心就好似大蛇丸咁<br />\n俾左咒印佐助（女大J) , 解放左佢潛在既力量 <br />\n令女大J 心甘情願咁跟隨大蛇丸"},{"pid":"11d42fb5779be4bfa1464be61a0dcdce0369ae06","tid":869433,"uid":129660,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:42:19.000Z","msg":"咁你一定係嗚人"},{"pid":"d38fb05684507b003b954f81e9c1818bdb8ea7c7","tid":869433,"uid":187108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:42:47.000Z","msg":"唯一共通點就係洗腦技術相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98805a91acf09332fd609c4d14dda9bb0e0223d1","tid":869433,"uid":209120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:44:15.000Z","msg":"咁女大J係咪識開須佐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3e430e71dbacc58f1910a4b2869e2baa33ce8d","tid":869433,"uid":170668,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:44:16.000Z","msg":"系。。。 好deserve我地respect skr skr skr 😂😂🤙🏻🤙🏻🤙🏻"},{"pid":"4c4b131d031b2683d6d703540cfbe1d9f989f41e","tid":869433,"uid":54930,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:45:25.000Z","msg":"死毒撚睇到上晒腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e77d51740485ff3bea6064be449c07daef5ab27","tid":869433,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-1